---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="关于" description="关于陈道雷 — 算电协同投资分析 · 专业背景">
  <a href="/" class="back-link">← 返回首页</a>

  <h1>关于</h1>

  <div class="intro-card">
    <div class="intro-avatar">陈</div>
    <div>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>陈道雷</strong> · 算电协同 / 电力交易 / 新能源基础设施投资</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 0; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem;">
        关注三个高度关联的领域：算力与电力的基础设施级协同、电力市场改革与交易、以及新能源基础设施投资。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>这个网站是做什么的？</h2>
  <p>这里是我输出专业思考的地方。不做泛泛的行业综述，只写自己真正有判断的内容——包括投资框架、政策解读、产业链拆解，以及方法论沉淀。</p>
  <p>当前重点方向是<strong>算电协同</strong>。算力正在成为新的电力需求，AI 算力集群的用电规模已进入 500MW 级。2026 年算电协同首次进入政府工作报告，这是一个处于政策窗口与产业爆发交汇点的主题。</p>

  <h2>内容主题</h2>
  <div class="topic-grid">
    <div class="topic-card" style="border-left-color: #0d9488;">
      <div class="topic-icon">⚡</div>
      <div>
        <strong>算电协同</strong>
        <p>算力与电力协同的政策、技术、商业模式与投资分析</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="topic-card" style="border-left-color: #2563eb;">
      <div class="topic-icon">📈</div>
      <div>
        <strong>电力交易</strong>
        <p>市场规则、交易策略、数据分析</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="topic-card" style="border-left-color: #7c3aed;">
      <div class="topic-icon">🔋</div>
      <div>
        <strong>新能源基础设施</strong>
        <p>充电网络、储能、绿色电力</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="topic-card" style="border-left-color: #d97706;">
      <div class="topic-icon">📊</div>
      <div>
        <strong>投资方法论</strong>
        <p>分析框架、模型方法、决策反思</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="topic-card" style="border-left-color: #6366f1;">
      <div class="topic-icon">🤖</div>
      <div>
        <strong>AI 协作效率</strong>
        <p>AI 辅助深度工作的方法与实践</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>历程</h2>
  <div class="timeline">

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <div class="timeline-date">2026-05</div>
        <div class="timeline-title">个人网站上线 · 持续输出算电协同深度内容</div>
        <div class="timeline-desc">搭建个人网站，系统性地拆解算电协同、六张网基础设施投资等方向。</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <div class="timeline-date">2025-2026</div>
        <div class="timeline-title">AI 协作工具开发 · 投资框架沉淀</div>
        <div class="timeline-desc">开发 PPT 质量审查工具、合同条款辅助工具，用 AI 大幅提升专业产出效率。沉淀可复用的投资分析框架。</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <div class="timeline-date">2023-2025</div>
        <div class="timeline-title">新能源基础设施投资 · 重卡超充网络</div>
        <div class="timeline-desc">聚焦重卡充电站投资分析，涉及选址模型、财务建模（NPV/IRR/DCF）、敏感性分析、竞价策略。</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <div class="timeline-date">2022-2023</div>
        <div class="timeline-title">电力市场改革研究 · 交易策略</div>
        <div class="timeline-desc">深度研究电力市场改革方向，关注现货市场、辅助服务、绿电交易等议题。</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <div class="timeline-date">2018-2022</div>
        <div class="timeline-title">基金投融资 · 协议文本 · 投资研究</div>
        <div class="timeline-desc">基金投资相关实务工作积累，包括路演材料、投资备忘录、协议/合同起草。</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <h2>联系</h2>
  <p>欢迎通过 <a href="https://github.com/David-Chen1977">GitHub</a> 联系，或订阅 <a href="/rss.xml">RSS</a> 关注更新。</p>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .intro-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .intro-avatar {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-accent));
    color: #fff;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .topic-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .topic-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border-left: 3px solid;
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
  }
  .topic-card p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
  .topic-card strong {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .topic-icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 8px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--color-accent), var(--color-primary));
    opacity: 0.3;
    border-radius: 1px;
  }
  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .timeline-item:last-child {
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }
  .timeline-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: -2rem;
    top: 4px;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-bg);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--color-accent);
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .timeline-content {
    padding-top: 0;
  }
  .timeline-date {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }
  .timeline-title {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }
  .timeline-desc {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
